Supplemental Readings
Science_Daily
A Web site devoted to daily briefings on science news, in all categories of
science.
Angier, Natalie. "Seeing_Red." The New York Times, February 6, 2007.
A short piece on the science of everyday life.
Sacks, Oliver. "Patterns." From the series "Migraine: Perspectives on a
Headache." The New York Times, February 13, 2008.
An excellent piece on the visual phenomenena accompanying migraines.
Dizikes, Peter. "Civic_Science." Boston Globe, April 30, 2006.
Contains a good discussion of scientific literacy.
